comments: Profe Yani is an angel. I took beginner Spanish and then went to Spain with her over Winter Term. She truly cares about all of her students and created an environment that was helpful and safe to make mistakes in. Stay up to date with the Supersite! Most of the classwork is outside of class, class is for practicing your new Spanish skills!
